Class AbstractSourcePathResolver

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DefaultSourcePathResolver, IjProjectSourcePathResolver
    public abstract class AbstractSourcePathResolver
extends Object
implements SourcePathResolver
    Abstract implementation of SourcePathResolver.

    Most of the SourcePathResolverAdapter interface can be implemented in terms of just a few functions ( the main requirement is resolving BuildTargetSourcePaths).

    Existing code may expect to resolve each SourcePath to only one Path. In such cases, SourcePathResolverAdapter is used to convert the resolver to return only one Path per SourcePath.
